  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nUser requested available domain names for a spirituality website based on 'eia' or 'eya'. Manus performed programmatic domain availability checks and identified 39 available options, providing categorized recommendations with 'eya-light.com' as the top choice due to its universal spiritual resonance and memorability.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nUser is developing a new spirituality-focused website and needed domain name suggestions that incorporate 'eia' or 'eya' while being both available and spiritually inspiring.\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nConducted comprehensive domain availability search using programmatic tools, categorized results by spiritual themes (light, sacred, awakening, journey, wisdom, space), and provided detailed analysis with ratings and recommendations.\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [domain_list] 39 Available Spirituality Domains — Comprehensive list of available domains categorized by spiritual themes with ratings and analysis\n- [recommendation] Top 3 Domain Recommendations — Curated selection with eya-light.com, sacred-eya.com, and eya-space.com as top choices\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Recommended eya-light.com as primary choice for universal appeal and memorability\n- Categorized domains by spiritual themes for easier selection\n- Prioritized non-denominational options for broader audience reach\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Programmatic domain checking worked effectively on iOS\n- Thematic categorization helped organize large number of options\n- Rating system provided clear comparison criteria\nDiscoveries:\n\n- Many spirituality-related domains still available in .com\n- Light-based domains have strong universal spiritual appeal\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- Final decision on which domain to register\n- Whether user prefers 'eia' or 'eya' variation\n- Budget considerations for premium domain options\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- User to review recommendations and make final domain selection\n- Register chosen domain before availability changes\n- Begin website development planning with selected domain\n---\nUID: jyUsdafiD7MaerNtkxYjrH | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0139\n"
